name: Name for the desired output directory, if inside a SessionConfig, directory will be placed within the session output dir
data: Array of all mp4 files to be analyzed in the running config

configurations.argOverride: Should console line arguments be overridden? Expected value is a boolean (without string marks '')

args.CommentValue: This is a comment value and should be removed. Args are used in the case that argOverride is true for default values leave these unchanged
